headline: Packaging Corp. (PKG) Misses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Packaging Corp. (PKG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -3.73% and -2.42%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
